    • 构造器详细资料

      • ProgressDialog

        private ProgressDialog()
        Display an error dialog and respective error message. Like other dialogs, this constructor is private, such that users can use only one dialog, i.e., ProgressDialog.progressDialog to display message. This is helpful for saving space (only one dialog) since we may need "many" dialogs.
